{"tid":1178386,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以為嫁中國有錢農場主人　一到家全幻滅「連廁所都不能用」秒離婚","createTime":"2019-05-30T11:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T13:16:11.000Z","uid":150609,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4dadd4eb8c4b1d4286cde60f7d6a679e326cfcf9","tid":1178386,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Jmp6SZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Jmp6SZ.png&h=3b23b15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名巴基斯坦新娘原本以為嫁給中國大陸有錢農場主人，從此脫離巴基斯坦的苦日子。然而到達當地才發現，原本的大農場只是一般農家的養鴨場，甚至沒有一間適合的廁所。這段婚姻只維持了短短 8 天，這位新娘在大使館的協助下辦理離婚手續，才順利返回家鄉。<br />\n<br />\n根據《紐約時報》報導，來自巴基斯坦古吉蘭瓦拉貧民區的拉比雅‧坎瓦爾（ Rabia Kanwal ）遇到從中國大陸籍來旅遊的張姓男子。張男表示自己是有錢的農場主人，更宣稱自己是穆斯林。坎瓦爾跟家人雖然和張姓男子語言不通，但數月來用翻譯軟體對話，雙方建立起感情基礎，之後坎瓦爾與張男就在巴基斯坦舉行婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n婚禮結束後，坎瓦爾和張男一起搬回中國。歷經長途跋涉到了中國大陸的山東省東張村，坎瓦爾發現張男只是養鴨的貧窮農民，更糟的是，他根本不是穆斯林！<br />\n<br />\n坎瓦爾表示，張男家裡甚至沒有適合穆斯林用的洗手間。坎瓦爾指控這家人將她鎖在房間 2 天防止她逃跑。她向巴基斯坦大使館傳電子郵件求救，終於受到幫忙順利回到家鄉，結束短短 8 天的婚姻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605dfd11f452b77d488f4ff117ebc2b628331e9b","tid":1178386,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eff0c07cf0a647d9df561faf4cb84481093c439","tid":1178386,"uid":230235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c916ea1058171910fd40ddf477d8009c65baef50","tid":1178386,"uid":248020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"都比人姦左8日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307847b983c4e1f32cb3b17bd9b0e8bc6013fbaa","tid":1178386,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c916ea1058171910fd40ddf477d8009c65baef50","tid":1178386,"uid":248020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"都比人姦左8日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"巴味奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64e0985481e84be4dbcf40234c3259e2b8a83e6","tid":1178386,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爛坦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a4afcfee08713ecdd6e5c88aa7319ef590d2fa","tid":1178386,"uid":60709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:15:44.000Z","msg":"走左個巴妹<br />\n似係會捉番個城市妹番去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7754d577fc90dff68bfd3f2503816d7e85cc6017","tid":1178386,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"白痴....有錢都唔娶你啦...貪你有味咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}